## Phase 27: Bot Ecosystem Expansion & Admin Management

This phase focuses on populating the platform with a high-fidelity bot workforce and providing admin tools for their management.

### Proposed Changes

#### [NEW] [create-bots/route.ts](file:///C:/GOLive/app/api/admin/create-bots/route.ts)
- POST endpoint that uses `supabase-js` service role to bulk create `Auth` users and `Profiles`.
- Generates 50 unique bot identities with randomized usernames and personas.

#### [NEW] [bots/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/admin/bots/page.tsx)
- A high-fidelity grid dashboard showing all "bot" users.
- Quick actions to update profile pics, bios, and engagement stats.

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/admin/layout.tsx)
- Add "Bot Management" to the admin sidebar.

### Verification Plan
